Miriam Sorrell is the blogger behind www.mouthwateringvegan.com.Born in London, Miriam is the creator and face of Mouthwatering Vegan, the enormously popular vegan food blog, and her Mouthwatering Vegan cookbook is published by Appetite (a Random House Canada imprint) in Spring 2013. Her food is all about enticing the senses, and in particular taking taste to another dimension. This is not altogether surprising, since she is also a photographer (and shoots all her own food pics), an established abstracts artist, and a jewelry designer. Miriam enjoys humour, creative thinking, good movies, music, photography, and, in her spare time, she is a compulsive bookworm. She has a 6 year old daughter and 4 cats, and currently resides in Malta with her husband Jonathan, a music composer and pianist.
